prompt: Show me the overall sales in the year 2024 for the top 4 selling items in store number 11 and 12 where the account type is RETAIL and also sales reprenative name
sql_query: SELECT   ITEM_NUMBER,   ITEM_DESCRIPTION,   SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES,   SALES_REP_NAME FROM   REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE WHERE   TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'   AND STORE_NUMBER IN ('11', '12')   AND ACCOUNT_TYPE_NAME = 'RETAIL' GROUP BY   ITEM_NUMBER,   ITEM_DESCRIPTION,   SALES_REP_NAME ORDER BY   TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 4;

sql_query: SELECT      V.STORE_NAME,     V.SALES_REP_NAME,     V.CATEGORY_NAME,     V.ITEM_DESCRIPTION AS BRAND_NAME,     AVG(CAST(V.GP_PERCENT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GROSS_PROFIT_MARGIN_PCT FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE V WHERE      V.GP_PERCENT IS NOT NULL      AND V.GP_PERCENT != '' GROUP BY      V.STORE_NAME,     V.SALES_REP_NAME,     V.CATEGORY_NAME,     V.ITEM_DESCRIPTION ORDER BY      GROSS_PROFIT_MARGIN_PCT DESC LIMIT 5;

prompt: What are the monthly revenue trends for the past year?

sql_query: WITH last_12_months AS (   SELECT DATEADD(MONTH, -12, DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', CURRENT_DATE())) AS start_date ) SELECT    v.TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,   v.TRANSACTION_MONTH_NAME,   SUM(CAST(v.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS MONTHLY_REVENUE,   SUM(CAST(v.DAILY_TOTAL_QUANTITY AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS MONTHLY_QUANTITY,   SUM(CAST(v.DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS MONTHLY_GROSS_PROFIT FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES v CROSS JOIN last_12_months l WHERE CAST(v.TRANSACTION_DT AS DATE) >= l.start_date GROUP BY    v.TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,   v.TRANSACTION_MONTH_NAME ORDER BY    v.TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH LIMIT 100

prompt: What are the monthly revenue trends for the past year?
sql_query: WITH last_12_months AS (    SELECT       TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,      TRANSACTION_MONTH_NAME,      SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS MONTHLY_REVENUE,      SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_QUANTITY AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS MONTHLY_QUANTITY    FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES    WHERE CAST(TRANSACTION_DT AS DATE) >= DATEADD(YEAR, -1, CURRENT_DATE())    GROUP BY       TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,      TRANSACTION_MONTH_NAME    ORDER BY       TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH DESC  )  SELECT * FROM last_12_months  LIMIT 12

sql_query: SELECT    STORE_NUMBER,    STORE_NAME,    SALES_REP_NUMBER,    SALES_REP_NAME,    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2025,    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2024,    (SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END)) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END), 0) * 100 AS YOY_GROWTH_PERCENTAGE  FROM    REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES  GROUP BY    STORE_NUMBER,    STORE_NAME,    SALES_REP_NUMBER,    SALES_REP_NAME  ORDER BY    YOY_GROWTH_PERCENTAGE DESC  LIMIT 100;

sql_query: SELECT    STORE_NAME,    SALES_REP_NAME,    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2025,    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2024,    (SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END)) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END), 0) * 100 AS SALES_GROWTH_PERCENTAGE  FROM    REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES  WHERE    TRANSACTION_YEAR IN ('2024', '2025')  GROUP BY    STORE_NAME,    SALES_REP_NAME  HAVING    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) > 0 AND    SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) > 0  ORDER BY    STORE_NAME,    SALES_REP_NAME  LIMIT 100;

prompt: Generate a comparison report of sales and gross profit (GP) for each store, showing both current year 2025 and previous year figures in single time.
sql_query: WITH CurrentYear AS (     SELECT          STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GP_2025     FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'     GROUP BY STORE_NUMBER, STORE_NAME ), PreviousYear AS (     SELECT          STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GP_2024     FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'     GROUP BY STORE_NUMBER, STORE_NAME ) SELECT      COALESCE(c.STORE_NUMBER, p.STORE_NUMBER) AS STORE_NUMBER,     COALESCE(c.STORE_NAME, p.STORE_NAME) AS STORE_NAME,     COALESCE(SALES_2025, 0) AS SALES_2025,     COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0) AS SALES_2024,     COALESCE(GP_2025, 0) AS GP_2025,     COALESCE(GP_2024, 0) AS GP_2024,     ((COALESCE(SALES_2025, 0) - COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0)) / NULLIF(COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0), 0) * 100) AS SALES_YOY_CHANGE_PCT,     ((COALESCE(GP_2025, 0) - COALESCE(GP_2024, 0)) / NULLIF(COALESCE(GP_2024, 0), 0) * 100) AS GP_YOY_CHANGE_PCT FROM CurrentYear c FULL OUTER JOIN PreviousYear p ON c.STORE_NUMBER = p.STORE_NUMBER ORDER BY COALESCE(c.STORE_NUMBER, p.STORE_NUMBER) LIMIT 100

prompt: Generate a comparison report of sales and gross profit (GP) for each store, showing both current year 2025 and previous year figures.
sql_query: WITH CurrentYear AS (     SELECT          STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GP_2025     FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'     GROUP BY STORE_NUMBER, STORE_NAME ), PreviousYear AS (     SELECT          STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GP_2024     FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'     GROUP BY STORE_NUMBER, STORE_NAME ) SELECT      COALESCE(c.STORE_NUMBER, p.STORE_NUMBER) AS STORE_NUMBER,     COALESCE(c.STORE_NAME, p.STORE_NAME) AS STORE_NAME,     COALESCE(SALES_2025, 0) AS SALES_2025,     COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0) AS SALES_2024,     COALESCE(GP_2025, 0) AS GP_2025,     COALESCE(GP_2024, 0) AS GP_2024,     ((COALESCE(SALES_2025, 0) - COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0)) / NULLIF(COALESCE(SALES_2024, 0), 0) * 100) AS SALES_YOY_CHANGE_PCT,     ((COALESCE(GP_2025, 0) - COALESCE(GP_2024, 0)) / NULLIF(COALESCE(GP_2024, 0), 0) * 100) AS GP_YOY_CHANGE_PCT FROM CurrentYear c FULL OUTER JOIN PreviousYear p ON c.STORE_NUMBER = p.STORE_NUMBER ORDER BY COALESCE(c.STORE_NUMBER, p.STORE_NUMBER) LIMIT 100

prompt: Show me the monthly trends for product categories over the past 2 years, including growth rates sort by total sales desc
sql_query: WITH base_data AS (   SELECT      TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,     CATEGORY_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS TOTAL_SALES,     LAG(SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2)))) OVER (PARTITION BY CATEGORY_NAME ORDER BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH) AS PREV_MONTH_SALES   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH >= TO_CHAR(DATEADD(YEAR, -2, CURRENT_DATE()), 'YYYY-MM')   GROUP BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, CATEGORY_NAME ) SELECT   TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH,   CATEGORY_NAME,   TOTAL_SALES,   CASE      WHEN PREV_MONTH_SALES > 0 THEN        ((TOTAL_SALES - PREV_MONTH_SALES) / PREV_MONTH_SALES) * 100     ELSE 0   END AS GROWTH_RATE FROM base_data ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC, TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH LIMIT 100

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s24.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s24.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s24.SALES_2024,   s25.SALES_2025,   ((s25.SALES_2025 - s24.SALES_2024) / s24.SALES_2024 * 100) AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s24 JOIN sales_2025 s25   ON s24.STORE_NUM_NAME = s25.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s24.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s25.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 100

sql_query: SELECT      T1.STORE_NUM_NAME,     T1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(T1.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2024,     SUM(CAST(T2.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2025,     (SUM(CAST(T2.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) - SUM(CAST(T1.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC))) /          NULLIF(SUM(CAST(T1.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)), 0) * 100 AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM      REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES T1 LEFT JOIN      REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES T2     ON T1.STORE_NUMBER = T2.STORE_NUMBER     AND T1.SALES_REP_NUMBER = T2.SALES_REP_NUMBER     AND T2.TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' WHERE      T1.TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' GROUP BY      T1.STORE_NUM_NAME,     T1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME HAVING      SALES_2024 > 0 ORDER BY      YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 5

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s1.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_2024,   s2.SALES_2025,   ((s2.SALES_2025 - s1.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s1.SALES_2024, 0) * 100) AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s1 JOIN sales_2025 s2   ON s1.STORE_NUM_NAME = s2.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s2.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH SALES_2024 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2024     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ), SALES_2025 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2025     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ) SELECT     s2025.STORE_NUMBER,     s2025.STORE_NAME,     s2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER,     s2025.SALES_REP_NAME,     s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024,     s2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025,     (s2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025 - s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024, 0) * 100 AS YEAR_OVER_YEAR_GROWTH_PERCENT FROM     SALES_2025 AS s2025 JOIN     SALES_2024 AS s2024 ON     s2025.STORE_NUMBER = s2024.STORE_NUMBER AND s2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER = s2024.SALES_REP_NUMBER ORDER BY     YEAR_OVER_YEAR_GROWTH_PERCENT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: SELECT     STORE_NUMBER,     STORE_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUMBER,     SALES_REP_NAME,     SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2024,     SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2025,     (SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END)) / NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC) ELSE 0 END), 0) * 100 AS YOY_GROWTH_PERCENT FROM     REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES WHERE     TRANSACTION_YEAR IN ('2024', '2025') GROUP BY     STORE_NUMBER,     STORE_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUMBER,     SALES_REP_NAME ORDER BY     YOY_GROWTH_PERCENT DESC LIMIT 3;

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s1.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_2024,   s2.SALES_2025,   ((s2.SALES_2025 - s1.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s1.SALES_2024, 0) * 100) AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s1 JOIN sales_2025 s2   ON s1.STORE_NUM_NAME = s2.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s2.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

prompt: Show me year-over-year sales growth by store and sales rep comparing 2025 to 2024 top 3
sql_query: WITH Sales2024 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2024     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ), Sales2025 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2025     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ) SELECT     S2025.STORE_NUMBER,     S2025.STORE_NAME,     S2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER,     S2025.SALES_REP_NAME,     S2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024,     S2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025,     (S2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025 - S2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024) / NULLIF(S2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024, 0) * 100 AS YOY_GROWTH_PERCENTAGE FROM     Sales2025 AS S2025 JOIN     Sales2024 AS S2024     ON S2025.STORE_NUMBER = S2024.STORE_NUMBER     AND S2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER = S2024.SALES_REP_NUMBER ORDER BY     YOY_GROWTH_PERCENTAGE DESC LIMIT 3;

prompt: Show me the top 10 sales representatives by total sales and total profit percentage for the last year
sql_query: WITH last_year AS (   SELECT DISTINCT TRANSACTION_YEAR   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   ORDER BY TRANSACTION_YEAR DESC   LIMIT 1 ) SELECT    s.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   SUM(CAST(s.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS TOTAL_SALES,   SUM(CAST(s.DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS TOTAL_PROFIT,   (SUM(CAST(s.DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) / NULLIF(SUM(CAST(s.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))), 0) * 100) AS PROFIT_PERCENTAGE FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES s WHERE s.TRANSACTION_YEAR = (SELECT TRANSACTION_YEAR FROM last_year) GROUP BY s.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 10

prompt: Show total revenue, gross profit, gross profit percentage for each store for 2025 Q1. Order by gross profit
sql_query: SELECT     STORE_NUM_NAME,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS TOTAL_REVENUE,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS GROSS_PROFIT,    (SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_GROSS_PROFIT AS DECIMAL(18,2))) / NULLIF(SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))), 0) * 100) AS GROSS_PROFIT_PCTFROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALESWHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'    AND TRANSACTION_QUARTER = '1'GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAMEORDER BY GROSS_PROFIT DESCLIMIT 100

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2024   FROM GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = 2024   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2025   FROM GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = 2025   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s24.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s24.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s24.SALES_2024,   s25.SALES_2025,   CAST((s25.SALES_2025 - s24.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s24.SALES_2024, 0) * 100 AS DECIMAL(10,2)) AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s24 JOIN sales_2025 s25   ON s24.STORE_NUM_NAME = s25.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s24.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s25.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2024   FROM GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = 2024   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS SALES_2025   FROM GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = 2025   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s1.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_2024,   s2.SALES_2025,   ((s2.SALES_2025 - s1.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s1.SALES_2024, 0)) * 100 AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s1 JOIN sales_2025 s2   ON s1.STORE_NUM_NAME = s2.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s2.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH SALES_2024 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2024     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ), SALES_2025 AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES_2025     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'     GROUP BY         STORE_NUMBER,         STORE_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUMBER,         SALES_REP_NAME ) SELECT     s2025.STORE_NUMBER,     s2025.STORE_NAME,     s2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER,     s2025.SALES_REP_NAME,     s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024,     s2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025,     (s2025.TOTAL_SALES_2025 - s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s2024.TOTAL_SALES_2024, 0) * 100 AS YEAR_OVER_YEAR_GROWTH_PERCENT FROM     SALES_2025 AS s2025 JOIN     SALES_2024 AS s2024 ON     s2025.STORE_NUMBER = s2024.STORE_NUMBER AND s2025.SALES_REP_NUMBER = s2024.SALES_REP_NUMBER ORDER BY     YEAR_OVER_YEAR_GROWTH_PERCENT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH sales_2024 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2024   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), sales_2025 AS (   SELECT      STORE_NUM_NAME,     SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS SALES_2025   FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES   WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025'   GROUP BY STORE_NUM_NAME, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT    s1.STORE_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,   s1.SALES_2024,   s2.SALES_2025,   ((s2.SALES_2025 - s1.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(s1.SALES_2024, 0) * 100) AS YOY_GROWTH_PCT FROM sales_2024 s1 JOIN sales_2025 s2   ON s1.STORE_NUM_NAME = s2.STORE_NUM_NAME   AND s1.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = s2.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY YOY_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH SalesByYear AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUM_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,         TRANSACTION_YEAR,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR IN ('2024', '2025')     GROUP BY         STORE_NUM_NAME,         SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,         TRANSACTION_YEAR ), YoYComparison AS (     SELECT         s.STORE_NUM_NAME,         s.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,         SUM(CASE WHEN s.TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' THEN s.TOTAL_SALES ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2024,         SUM(CASE WHEN s.TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2025' THEN s.TOTAL_SALES ELSE 0 END) AS SALES_2025     FROM         SalesByYear s     GROUP BY         s.STORE_NUM_NAME,         s.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT     yoy.STORE_NUM_NAME,     yoy.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME,     yoy.SALES_2024,     yoy.SALES_2025,     (yoy.SALES_2025 - yoy.SALES_2024) / NULLIF(yoy.SALES_2024, 0) * 100 AS YOY_SALES_GROWTH_PCT FROM     YoYComparison yoy WHERE     yoy.SALES_2024 IS NOT NULL AND yoy.SALES_2025 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY     YOY_SALES_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 3

sql_query: WITH StoreYearlySales AS (     SELECT         STORE_NUM_NAME,         TRANSACTION_YEAR,         SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS CURRENT_YEAR_SALES     FROM         REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES     WHERE         TRANSACTION_YEAR IN ('2023', '2024')     GROUP BY         STORE_NUM_NAME,         TRANSACTION_YEAR ) SELECT     s.STORE_NUM_NAME,     s.TRANSACTION_YEAR,     s.CURRENT_YEAR_SALES,     LAG(s.CURRENT_YEAR_SALES, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY s.STORE_NUM_NAME ORDER BY s.TRANSACTION_YEAR) AS PREVIOUS_YEAR_SALES,     (s.CURRENT_YEAR_SALES - LAG(s.CURRENT_YEAR_SALES, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY s.STORE_NUM_NAME ORDER BY s.TRANSACTION_YEAR)) / NULLIF(LAG(s.CURRENT_YEAR_SALES, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY s.STORE_NUM_NAME ORDER BY s.TRANSACTION_YEAR), 0) * 100 AS SALES_GROWTH_PCT FROM     StoreYearlySales s WHERE     s.TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' ORDER BY     SALES_GROWTH_PCT DESC LIMIT 4

sql_query: WITH all_reps AS ( SELECT DISTINCT REP_NAME AS SALES_REP FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI UNION SELECT DISTINCT SALES_REP_NAME FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI UNION SELECT DISTINCT SALES_REP_NAME FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI),rep_counts AS ( SELECT SALES_REP, SUM(CASE WHEN EXISTS_IN_ALL_REP = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN EXISTS_IN_BOOKING = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN EXISTS_IN_SALES = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS VIEW_COUNT FROM ( SELECT ar.SALES_REP, CASE WHEN vak.REP_NAME IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS EXISTS_IN_ALL_REP, CASE WHEN vbk.SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS EXISTS_IN_BOOKING, CASE WHEN vsk.SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS EXISTS_IN_SALES FROM all_reps ar LEFT JOIN PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI vak ON ar.SALES_REP = vak.REP_NAME LEFT JOIN PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI vbk ON ar.SALES_REP = vbk.SALES_REP_NAME LEFT JOIN PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI vsk ON ar.SALES_REP = vsk.SALES_REP_NAME ) GROUP BY SALES_REP)SELECT VIEW_COUNT AS VIEWS_PRESENT_IN, COUNT(*) AS NUMBER_OF_REPS FROM rep_counts GROUP BY VIEW_COUNT ORDER BY VIEW_COUNT LIMIT 5

sql_query: WITH AllReps AS (     SELECT         REP_NAME AS SALES_REP_NAME,         'VW_ALL_REP_KPI' AS SOURCE_VIEW     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI     WHERE REP_NAME IS NOT NULL      UNION ALL      SELECT         SALES_REP_NAME AS SALES_REP_NAME,         'VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI' AS SOURCE_VIEW     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI     WHERE SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL      UNION ALL      SELECT         SALES_REP_NAME AS SALES_REP_NAME,         'VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI' AS SOURCE_VIEW     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI     WHERE SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL ), DistinctRepsPerView AS (     SELECT DISTINCT         SALES_REP_NAME,         SOURCE_VIEW     FROM AllReps ) SELECT     SALES_REP_NAME,     COUNT(DISTINCT SOURCE_VIEW) AS NUMBER_OF_VIEWS_APPEARING_IN FROM DistinctRepsPerView GROUP BY     SALES_REP_NAME HAVING     COUNT(DISTINCT SOURCE_VIEW) > 1 ORDER BY     NUMBER_OF_VIEWS_APPEARING_IN DESC,     SALES_REP_NAME LIMIT 5

prompt: What is the revenue performance ranking of sales representatives, and what are the revenue ranges for top performers versus developing performers?
sql_query: WITH sales_rep_performance AS ( SELECT SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME, SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS TOTAL_REVENUE, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) DESC) AS REVENUE_RANK, -- Calculate quartiles for performance segmentation NTILE(4) OVER (ORDER BY SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) DESC) AS PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES WHERE SALES_REP_NUMBER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME ) SELECT SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME, TOTAL_REVENUE, REVENUE_RANK, CASE WHEN PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE = 1 THEN 'Top Performer' WHEN PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE = 2 THEN 'Strong Performer' WHEN PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE = 3 THEN 'Moderate Performer' ELSE 'Developing Performer' END AS PERFORMANCE_CATEGORY, MIN(TOTAL_REVENUE) OVER (PARTITION BY PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE) AS CATEGORY_MIN_REVENUE, MAX(TOTAL_REVENUE) OVER (PARTITION BY PERFORMANCE_QUARTILE) AS CATEGORY_MAX_REVENUE FROM sales_rep_performance ORDER BY REVENUE_RANK LIMIT 100;

prompt: What is the revenue performance ranking of sales representatives, and what are the revenue ranges for top performers versus developing performers?
sql_query: SELECT    REP_NAME,    REP_REVENUE_RANK,    CASE      WHEN REP_PERFORMANCE_TIER = 'Top Performer' THEN 'Top Performer'      WHEN REP_PERFORMANCE_TIER = 'Developing Performer' THEN 'Developing Performer'      ELSE 'Other'    END AS PERFORMANCE_CATEGORY,    TOTAL_WON_REVENUE_SUPPORTED  FROM    PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI  ORDER BY    REP_REVENUE_RANK  LIMIT 100;

prompt: "How many distinct sales representatives are present across all three views, and which representatives appear in multiple views?
sql_query: SELECT      REP_NAME,      COUNT(DISTINCT TABLE_NAME) AS VIEW_COUNT FROM (     SELECT REP_NAME, 'VW_ALL_REP_KPI' AS TABLE_NAME     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI     WHERE REP_NAME IS NOT NULL     UNION ALL     SELECT SALES_REP_NAME AS REP_NAME, 'VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI' AS TABLE_NAME     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_BOOKING_REVENUE_ANALYTICS_KPI     WHERE SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL     UNION ALL     SELECT SALES_REP_NAME AS REP_NAME, 'VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI' AS TABLE_NAME     FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI     WHERE SALES_REP_NAME IS NOT NULL ) AS ALL_REPS GROUP BY REP_NAME HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT TABLE_NAME) > 1 LIMIT 10;

prompt: "How many distinct sales representatives are present across all table, and which representatives appear in multiple views?
sql_query: WITH sales_reps_daily AS ( SELECT DISTINCT SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME, 'V_SMM_DAILY_SALES' AS SOURCE_TABLE FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES ), sales_reps_item AS ( SELECT DISTINCT SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME, 'V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE' AS SOURCE_TABLE FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE ), combined_reps AS ( SELECT SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT SOURCE_TABLE) AS TABLE_COUNT, LISTAGG(SOURCE_TABLE, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY SOURCE_TABLE) AS APPEARS_IN FROM ( SELECT * FROM sales_reps_daily UNION ALL SELECT * FROM sales_reps_item ) GROUP BY SALES_REP_NUMBER, SALES_REP_NAME ) SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT SALES_REP_NUMBER) AS TOTAL_DISTINCT_REPS, SUM(CASE WHEN TABLE_COUNT > 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REPS_IN_MULTIPLE_VIEWS, SUM(CASE WHEN TABLE_COUNT = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REPS_IN_SINGLE_VIEW FROM combined_reps LIMIT 10

prompt: Show me the top 8 representatives by total items sold by each months in year2024
sql_query: WITH monthly_sales AS ( SELECT TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME, SUM(CAST(QUANTITY AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' GROUP BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ), ranked_reps AS ( SELECT SALES_REP_NUM_NAME, SUM(TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD) AS TOTAL_ITEMS FROM monthly_sales GROUP BY SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY TOTAL_ITEMS DESC LIMIT 8 ) SELECT ms.TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, ms.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME, ms.TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD FROM monthly_sales ms INNER JOIN ranked_reps rr ON ms.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME = rr.SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ORDER BY ms.TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, ms.TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD DESC

prompt: Display the top 8 representatives with the highest item sales for every month in 2024.

prompt: Display the top 8 representatives with the highest item sales for every month in 2024 limit100.
sql_query: WITH RankedSales AS ( SELECT TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME, SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH ORDER BY SUM(CAST(DAILY_SALES AS NUMERIC)) DESC) AS rank FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_ITEM_DAILY_SALE WHERE TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024' GROUP BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME ) SELECT TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, SALES_REP_NUM_NAME, TOTAL_SALES FROM RankedSales WHERE rank <= 8 ORDER BY TRANSACTION_YEAR_MONTH, TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 100

sql_query: SELECT    STORE_NUMBER,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_QUANTITY AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SOLD  FROM    REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES  WHERE    TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'  GROUP BY    STORE_NUMBER  ORDER BY    TOTAL_QUANTITY_SOLD DESC  LIMIT 8;

prompt: Show the top 8 stores by total quantity of items sold in 2024
sql_query: SELECT    STORE_NAME,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_QUANTITY AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY  FROM    REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES  WHERE    TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'  GROUP BY    STORE_NAME  ORDER BY    TOTAL_QUANTITY DESC  LIMIT 8;

prompt: Show the top 8 stores by total quantity of items sold and total sales in 2024 give line chart
sql_query: SELECT    STORE_NAME,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_QUANTITY AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,    SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES  FROM    REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES  WHERE    TRANSACTION_YEAR = '2024'  GROUP BY    STORE_NAME  ORDER BY    TOTAL_QUANTITY DESC  LIMIT 8;

prompt: Show the top 8 stores by total quantity of items sold and total sales in 2024 give line chart
sql_query: SELECT    REP_FIRM AS STORE_NAME,    SUM(TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES_SUPPORTED) AS TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD,    SUM(TOTAL_WON_REVENUE_SUPPORTED) AS TOTAL_SALES  FROM    PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_ALL_REP_KPI  WHERE    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM REPORT_GENERATED_DATE) = 2024  GROUP BY    REP_FIRM  ORDER BY    TOTAL_ITEMS_SOLD DESC  LIMIT 8;

prompt: Show the top 8 stores by total quantity of items sold and total sales in 2024 give line chart
sql_query: SELECT store_id, store_name, SUM(profit) AS total_profit FROM sales GROUP BY store_id, store_name ORDER BY total_profit DESC LIMIT 2;

prompt: Show the top 8 stores by total quantity of items sold and total sales in 2024 give line chart
sql_query: WITH sales_data AS ( SELECT SALES_REP_NAME, SUM(CAST(WON_REVENUE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_SALES, SUM(CAST(WON_OPPORTUNITIES AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_SALES_PERFORMANCE_KPI WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM REPORT_GENERATED_DATE) = 2024 GROUP BY SALES_REP_NAME ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 8 ) SELECT SALES_REP_NAME, TOTAL_SALES, TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES FROM sales_data ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC
